OL,3,CMan jailed for careless driving that
OL,4,Ckilled young engaged couple
OL,6,FA man whose driving led to the deaths
OL,7,Fof an engaged couple who were
OL,8,Fpassengers in his car has been jailed.
OL,10,FBradley Clough, 25, was driving with
OL,11,Fseven passengers in his five-seater
OL,12,Fcar on Perham Down Road in Wiltshire
OL,13,Fwhen he skidded off the road and
OL,14,Fcrashed into trees, in October 2021.
OL,16,FCouple Jack Paolucci, 19, and Courtney
OL,17,FJennings, 18, died at the scene.
OL,19,FTwo other passengers also suffered
OL,20,Fserious injuries in the collision.
