OL,6,FAn investigation found that the
OL,7,Fvehicle Clough was driving was
OL,8,Foverloaded and one of the tyres was
OL,9,Funder-inflated.
OL,11,FFollowing a trial, Clough, of Burnley
OL,12,FRoad, Lancashire, was jailed for three
OL,13,Fyears for two counts of causing death
OL,14,Fby careless driving on 8 February at
OL,15,FWinchester Crown Court
OL,17,FThe families of Courtney and Jack
OL,18,Fsaid: "It is still impossible to
OL,19,Fcomprehend, understand or see a way
OL,20,Fforward without the light Courtney and
OL,21,FJack brought to our lives.
