OL,3,CMan jailed for careless driving that
OL,4,Ckilled young engaged couple
OL,6,F"Such a tragic night that has affected
OL,7,Fthe lives of numerous families.
OL,9,F"Some of the heartbreak would have
OL,10,Fbeen eased by truth and remorse from
OL,11,FBradley for an action that cost us so
OL,12,Fmuch.
OL,14,F"But unfortunately, that was not to be.
OL,16,F"However, we are thankful that after
OL,17,Ftwo years and three months we have
OL,18,Fsome justice and Bradley Clough gets
OL,19,Fthe reflection time in prison it's so
OL,20,Fclear he needs.
