OL,3,CMan jailed for careless driving that
OL,4,Ckilled young engaged couple
OL,6,F"As the two families of Courtney and
OL,7,FJack, we remain bound by the love they
OL,8,Fshared for each other and provide each
OL,9,Fother the strength needed to manage
OL,10,Feach day as one family.
OL,12,F"For our children, we will be forever
OL,13,Fproud and grateful that you chose us
OL,14,Fto be your parents.
OL,16,F"We would like to ask parents to
OL,17,Feducate their children on the dangers
OL,18,Fof being in an over laden car without
OL,19,Fa seatbelt.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
