OL,3,CMan jailed for careless driving that
OL,4,Ckilled young engaged couple
OL,6,F"It is important too, when your child
OL,7,Fstarts to drive, that they understand
OL,8,Fthe responsibility the privilege of
OL,9,Fdriving comes with and the essential
OL,10,Frequirement for maintaining their
OL,11,Fvehicle properly.
OL,13,F"If Courtney and Jack can help one
OL,14,Fother family not to suffer like we
OL,15,Fhave, our loss won't have been in
OL,16,Fvain."
