OL,6,FInvestigating officer Rachel Catling,
OL,7,Fof Wiltshire Police, said: "Clough's
OL,8,Factions were incredibly reckless and
OL,9,Firresponsible, leading to two young
OL,10,Fpeople tragically losing their lives.
OL,12,F"Jack and Courtney, who were engaged,
OL,13,Fhad their whole lives and promising
OL,14,Fcareers in the army ahead of them.
OL,16,F"I would like to pay tribute to them
OL,17,Fand their parents who have behaved
OL,18,Fwith dignity and respect throughout
OL,19,Fthis lengthy process despite the
OL,20,Fsignificant amount of pain that they
OL,21,Fmust be experiencing.
