OL,3,CMan jailed for careless driving that
OL,4,Ckilled young engaged couple
OL,6,F"Clough should have been well aware of
OL,7,Fhow dangerous his car was to drive.
OL,8,FNot only that, he lied during
OL,9,Finterview, claiming to be blinded by
OL,10,Fthe headlights of an oncoming vehicle.
OL,12,F"CCTV footage showed there was no
OL,13,Fother vehicle nearby at the time of
OL,14,Fthe collision.
OL,16,F"I am pleased he has been jailed for
OL,17,Fhis actions and I hope the families of
OL,18,FJack and Courtney can get some sort of
OL,19,Fsense of closure and begin to rebuild
OL,20,Ftheir lives."
